'''Final Fantasy Mystic Quest''' (known as '''Mystic Quest Legend''' in Europe and '''Final Fantasy USA: Mystic Quest''' in Japan) is an action RPG designed as an introductory RPG for Western audiences.

==Overview==

A simplified RPG featuring:
* Action-oriented gameplay with visible enemies
* No random encounters
* Weapons affect overworld obstacles
* Partner character system
* Simplified menu and equipment system

